							| 'Sponge mode', what is that supposed to mean? Since catching the coding bug, I am soaking in every little bit of knowledge I can get my hands on. How I ended up as a sponge? Well, let me tell you..
						p
							| In late 2016, while being a Digital Marketing Manager for adidas in Amsterdam, I found myself gravitating more and more towards technology. Mainly working on (amazing) campaign concepts, I missed a closer connection to websites and apps. At the same time, I started a weekly Creative Coding course at 
							span.underlined
